menu "Miner options"

    config MINER_USE_XTENSA_SHA256
        bool "Use the hand-written Xtensa assembly SHA-256 compression"
        default n
        help
            When enabled, the SHA-256 block compression uses the hand-written
            Xtensa assembly in core/sha256_compress_xtensa.S. When disabled (the
            default), the portable C version is used; the compiler schedules it
            slightly faster, so C is the default. Both live in the tree and this
            only chooses which one is built. The on-device self-test validates
            whichever is selected.

endmenu